      <div class="mv-card vision">
        <span class="label">Vision</span>
        <span class="sub">What success looks like</span>
        <h3>Woven into the fabric<br>of daily community life.</h3>
        <p>
          A southern Lewis County where the Christian Community Center is part
          of everyday life — where our facility is a blessing to every neighbor,
