<!-- VALUES -->
<section class="values-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">Our values</span>
        <h2 style="margin-top:1.2rem;">How we behave<br>when it's hard.</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="lead">
        Five convictions that shape every decision we make — where we invest,
        who we serve, and how we show up for our neighbors.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="value-row">
      <span class="num">— 01</span>
      <h3>Rooted Here.</h3>
      <p>
        We are not a regional church, a missions church, or a destination
        church. We are southern Lewis County's church. Every decision we
        make — where we invest, who we serve, where we show up — is filtered
        through one question: does this bless our community?
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="value-row">
      <span class="num">— 02</span>
      <h3>Relationship Before Proclamation.</h3>
      <p>
        We earn the right to be heard by being genuinely present. We build
        friendships first, not as a strategy, but because that's how Jesus
        moved through the world. Evangelism here looks like being a good
        neighbor for a long time.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="value-row">
      <span class="num">— 03</span>
      <h3>The Facility is Ministry.</h3>
      <p>
        Our building is not only where the church meets. It is an instrument
        of mission, open daily to a community that needs it. Every group
        that walks through our doors is a neighbor we're privileged to
        serve — and a relationship we're called to cultivate.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="value-row">
      <span class="num">— 04</span>
      <h3>Vibrant Over Predictable.</h3>
      <p>
        Humdrum Christianity is not who we are. We bring energy, spontaneity,
        and life to everything we do — especially worship — because a
        community that's never been in a church should encounter something
        worth coming back to.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="value-row">
      <span class="num">— 05</span>
      <h3>From Conversion to Conviction.</h3>
      <p>
        A new Christian is a beginning, not a finish line. We celebrate every
        first step of faith and then walk alongside people until that faith
        becomes deep, resilient, and fully their own.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- OFFERINGS -->
<section class="offerings-list">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">What we do</span>
        <h2 style="margin-top:1.2rem;">Worship, discipleship,<br>and an open door.</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="lead">
        Three ways our mission takes shape week to week — Sunday gatherings,
        weekly discipleship for students, and a facility that serves our
        neighbors all week long.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="offer-row">
      <span class="num">— 01</span>
      <h3>Sunday Worship</h3>
      <p>Join us every Sunday at <strong>10:00 AM</strong> for vibrant, Scripture-rooted worship. Whether you've been in church your whole life or have never set foot in one, there's a seat for you.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="offer-row">
      <span class="num">— 02</span>
      <h3>Youth Group</h3>
      <p>Weekly discipleship for students — games, friendships, honest conversation, and teaching that takes young people seriously. <strong>Thursdays, 6:30–8:30 PM</strong>, September through June.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="offer-row">
      <span class="num">— 03</span>
      <h3>The Facility</h3>
      <p>Our gym and facilities are available to families, groups, and neighbors across southern Lewis County. Birthdays, practices, reunions, meetings — if you need a room, we're glad to offer ours.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

